<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,222,390]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,273,295,319]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Notes.</emphasis>
Larva undescribed, but reared by 
<bibRefCitation author="Dufour" box="[652,814,294,318]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Dufour, L. (1848) Histoire des metamorphoses du Cheilosia aerea. Annales des Sciences Naturelles, Serie Zoologie 3, 9, 205 - 209." type="journal article" year="1848">
Dufour (
<number box="[748,806,294,318]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1848.0">1848</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
from among decaying leaves of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pulverulentum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Verbascum pulverulentum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and by 
<bibRefCitation author="Doczkal" box="[288,479,330,354]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Doczkal, D. (1996 b) Observations on host plants and behaviour of egg-laying females of Cheilosia Meigen (Diptera, Syrphidae) in central Europe. Volucella, 2, 77 - 85." type="journal article" year="1996" yearSuffix="b">
Doczkal (
<number box="[398,456,330,354]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1996.0">1996</number>
b)
</bibRefCitation>
from 
<taxonomicName box="[552,765,331,355]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nigrum">
<emphasis box="[552,765,331,355]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Verbascum nigrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Both 
<taxonomicName box="[844,964,331,355]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[844,964,331,355]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Verbascum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species are recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[1279,1358,330,354]" name="Greece" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Greece</collectingCountry>
(Flora Europaea 
<number box="[263,323,366,390]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="2010.0">2010</number>
), but are not included in the eight 
<taxonomicName box="[706,826,366,390]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" genus="Verbascum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[706,826,366,390]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Verbascum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species known from Lesvos (
<bibRefCitation author="Chilton" box="[1162,1314,366,390]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Chilton, L. (2011) Plant list from Lesvos. Marengo (publisher), Hunstanton, UK, 36 pp." type="book" year="2011">
Chilton 
<number box="[1255,1314,366,390]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="2011.0">2011</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
